casebody.data:
STATE of New Jersey, Plaintiff,
v.
R.H., Defendant-Movant. M-I25/126 September Term 2018
080737 Supreme Court of New Jersey. October 5, 2018

ORDER

It is ORDERED that the motion for leave to file a notice of petition for certification as within time (M-125) is denied; and it is further

ORDERED that the motion for leave to proceed as an indigent (M-126) is granted; and it is further

ORDERED that the notice of petition for certification is dismissed.
